metadata.name: Heimþrá
metadata.description:
seas call me home to you  
currents collide in your eyes  
behind that perfect shade of blue  
storms on the horizon  
light your iris with the lightning

dream over an ocean between us  
drums of a heartbeat and a promise  
you’ll never be without me for long  
goodbye doesn’t mean i’m gone  
i love you now, then, here, and all along  
your arms are the only place 
i don't feel alone
